Newly opened Tootles & French Wine Bar & Cafe in Astoria NY has a seasonal menu that offers cuisine that’s hard to find anywhere else in the US like Bone Marrow with fried Shallots & Chives, Wild Boar Sausage & Quail Lollipops. Wine pairing dinners, fresh curated charcuterie boards & private room dining are offered. There is an exquisite selection of specialty vermouths, apéritifs, digestifs, brandies, cognacs, armagnacs & wine pairing suggestions from owner & Sommelier Chad Goldsmith. Open for Brunch, Lunch & Dinner.
